data.text:
Dharma Kshetram

Benarjee (Balakrishna) is an advocate who hails from a respectable family and believes in law and order and fights against crime that prevails because of two rowdies Durga Prasad (Rami Reddy) and Pandu (Devan) who are mutual rivals. Complications arise when both Durga Prasad and Pandu join politics and become friends. Dharma Kshetram shows how Benarjee fights all odds to save justice.
